f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔係咁理解<br />\n<br />\n第一的人相比係二的人，做野係比較有智慧:<br />\n<br />\n因為你唔知好唔好食 + 食幾多會飽，你一野就切晒的話，到最後食兩舊就浪費左時間同資源去作無謂的準備。適合做老闆同涉及創意同用腦的職位<br />\n<br />\n第二的人:<br />\n呢d人多數係一隻&ldquo;牛&ldquo;，唔識變通，乜都死跟規則，無創意，但勝在勤力拼命。適合做工作一些比較基層的用勞力又唔用腦的工種。"},{"pid":"5e27430a837963811fae8227c759e5578809588d","tid":585162,"uid":141746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"不嬲成舊吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e57b5d124c4b852ae0275f2e4c2dfebbfd48fae","tid":585162,"uid":11977,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"切定一舊舊 d肉汁流撚哂出黎<br />\n一睇就知係唔撚識食又扮講究既垃圾"},{"pid":"eb813f2bf273b6522a15c982684231d0b9775739","tid":585162,"uid":30006,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:11:20.000Z","msg":"再補充，一塊靚牛扒一早切晒，流失肉汁；鐵板更甚，甚至overcook，咁簡單的道理都唔明的人，仲點請得落手"},{"pid":"dd023509fd112a52417c71f24d07b8835d352137","tid":585162,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:12:01.000Z","msg":"點睇免治牛？"},{"pid":"42291ef9e7374165b4dc36b7396bae462a0788b0","tid":585162,"uid":46336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"係唔係有準備既人就唔知喇<br />\n不過一定係唔識餐桌禮儀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155fa555ae53bee338fa98235af4ebfd2cddf8cb","tid":585162,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"我鐵板都食埋"},{"pid":"8f62be1cd365596f7e0c975650c2204bdc9a2f81","tid":585162,"uid":21488,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"17bcbb34a4509503bcf7241bcfb114231ea71e88","tid":585162,"uid":30006,"like":54,"dislike":4,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"3c8dec07d733976751cc804ecb829066cca3ec04","tid"